reviews.body:
@seanpdoyle I really love this approach! And I think it would be a good addition to the Action Mailer test framework.

One aspect of the design I'm curious about: why not have `assert_part` yield decoded content by default?

To me encoded content seems like it would be the dominant use case, especially since it works so well with the rails-dom-testing assertions.

